title: Form G-28 Was Rejected Because It Was Improperly Filed
body: On March 24, 2021, we rejected your Form G-28, Notice of Entry of Appearance as Attorney or Accredited Representative, Receipt Number YSC2190116070, because it was not filed correctly. If you wish to be represented, please contact your attorney or accredited representative to submit a new Form G-28 to the USCIS location where your case is pending. For more information on filing a Form G-28, please visit http://www.uscis.gov/forms/filing-your-form-g-28. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
